--- .gitignore (原始)


+++ .gitignore (修改后)
```
# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.Python
env/
venv/
.venv/
.ENV
.env
.env.*
.env.local

# Logs
*.log

# Temporary files
*.tmp
*.swp
*.swo

# OS generated files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Coverage reports
coverage/
htmlcov/
.coverage

# Testing
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/

# Build directories
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/

# VSCode
.vscode/

# Compressed files
*.zip
*.gz
*.tar
*.tgz
*.bz2
*.xz
*.7z
*.rar
*.zst
*.lz4
*.lzh
*.cab
*.arj
*.rpm
*.deb
*.Z
*.lz
*.lzo
```